title: Dakine AMP 12L Bike Pack
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2013 AMP 12L Bike Pack in Blue.
AMP 12L Bike Pack Features:
- 100 oz. / 3L Shape-Loc hydration reservoir
- Air Mesh suspended back panel
- Deployable helmet carry
- Mesh side pockets
- Fleece lined padded phone pocket
- Fleece
